<div id='communityQuestionsWithAnswers'>
<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/288215-has-anyone-else-read-this-gem-i-live-in">Has anyone else read this gem? I live in Australia, and no one seems to know of it here. It is now my favourite ever book. It is a big call, but I say it with confidence. Never have I seen a fantasy world so quirky, imaginative, unexpected. Never have characters been so kooky, twisted, lovely, creepy. This book is utterly absent of platitudes and cliches. It is like nothing else. I don&#39;t know what else I can say!</a>
</div>
