<a href="/questions/175885-i-m-really-interested-to-know-the-original">I&#39;m really interested to know the original German names for the characters. I thought the English names were wonderful so it made me interested to know how much of the invention to credit to the translator. So I&#39;m wondering if there is some Walter Moers tribute site that shows the original names side by side with the English. I&#39;ll be a-hunting</a>
