<div id="review_2506055297" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2506055297" />
    <a title="Ann-Marie &quot;Cookie M.&quot;" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/58567012-ann-marie-cookie-m"><img alt="Ann-Marie &quot;Cookie M.&quot;" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1607273374p2/58567012.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2506055297?book_show_action=true">Jun 13, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Ann-Marie &quot;Cookie M.&quot;" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Ann-Marie &quot;Cookie M.&quot;" href="/user/show/58567012-ann-marie-cookie-m">Ann-Marie &quot;Cookie M.&quot;</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Audio CD 9781441732583" href="/book/show/17293843-the-131-2-lives-of-captain-bluebear">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2506055297" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13496093106556952877">A delightful fairy tale for grownups skillfully translated from German so none of the humor is lost.<br/> This is first in a series of books by Walter Moers about the fantastic world of Zamonia.<br/> I listened to the audio book version, read expertly by Bronson Pinchot. This was a book that gave him reign to stretch his vocal and comedic talents and is worth the price if you are looking for a fun first entry into the world of audio books.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


